const data = pages.map(b=>b["HbA1c"]);

const chartData = {
    type: 'line',
    data: {        
		labels: labels.values,
        datasets: [{
            label: 'HbA1c (%) [<=5.6]',
            data: data.values,
            backgroundColor: [
                'rgba(255, 99, 132, 0.2)'
            ],
            borderColor: [
